asset.hookText:
A shipment of skateboarding history has arrived in New York City. The Nike SB Skate Safari pays homage to the city's most legendary spots: Brooklyn Banks, OG Seaport benches, and Pyramid Ledges to name a few.  Don't miss out. Pre- register now at http://www.skatesafarinyc.com. 

www.NikeSkateboarding.com
